{"type":"text","timestamp":1773439991697,"sessionID":"ses_316be8c08ffeZXbNAgwvZBSoRI","part":{"id":"prt_ce942160f002TMTk7Ru2AqorHm","sessionID":"ses_316be8c08ffeZXbNAgwvZBSoRI","messageID":"msg_ce9420993001cXjKP5nAiRw1B7","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nImplement the \"Dynamic agent-worker types from agency-agents registry\" feature (`dynamic-agent-types`) for the wombo-combo AI agent orchestration system. This feature allows users to specify different agent types per task, pulled dynamically from the `msitarzewski/agency-agents` GitHub repository, cached locally, and converted to woco-compatible agent definitions.\n\n## Instructions\n\n- **Feature spec is in the task prompt** at the top of the conversation — it defines constraints, forbidden actions, build verification, commit guidelines, and execution steps.\n- Must pull agent definitions from `https://github.com/msitarzewski/agency-agents` dynamically (NOT bundle them statically)\n- Must convert agency-agents format to woco's agent template format (markdown files in `.opencode/agents/`)\n- Must cache pulled agents locally in `.wombo-combo/agents-cache/` (separate from `.opencode/agents/` which is the active install dir)\n- Must support per-task agent type selection via task YAML `agent` field or `--agent` CLI flag\n- Must support offline mode using cached agents\n- Fallback: if agent not found, warn and fall back to `generalist-agent.md`; if registry unreachable, use cached agents\n- Cache TTL is configurable (default 24h)\n- Registry mode can be \"auto\", \"monitored\", or \"disabled\" via config\n- Use conventional commits, commit after each logical unit\n- Do NOT push to remote, do NOT modify `tasks` directory\n- Run `bun run build` to verify at end\n- Working directory: `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types`\n\n## Discoveries\n\n**The feature is ALREADY LARGELY IMPLEMENTED.** After thorough exploration, all major components exist:\n\n1. **`src/lib/agent-registry.ts`** (567 lines) — Complete implementation with:\n   - `resolveAgentForTask()` — resolves agent for a task with cache+TTL+offline fallback\n   - `prepareAgentDefinitions()` — batch resolution for all tasks in a wave\n   - `fetchAgent()` — fetches from GitHub raw URLs\n   - `listRegistryAgents()` — lists all available agents via GitHub Contents API\n   - `getCachedAgents()` — lists locally cached agents\n   - Cache operations: `cacheAgent()`, `getCachedAgent()`, `isCacheValid()`\n   - `writeAgentToWorktree()` — writes patched agent to worktree's `.opencode/agents/`\n   - `isSpecializedAgent()` — type guard for resolved vs generalist\n\n2. **`src/lib/format-converter.ts`** (410 lines) — Complete format conversion:\n   - `isAgencyAgentFormat()` — detects agency-agents format by frontmatter heuristics\n   - `parseAgencyAgent()` — parses agency-agents markdown structure\n   - `convertAgencyToWoco()` — converts to woco format (frontmatter with `description`+`mode`, clean body)\n   - `normalizeAgentFormat()` — convenience detect+convert entry point\n\n3. **`src/lib/templates.ts`** (433 lines) — Already integrated:\n   - `patchImportedAgent()` calls `normalizeAgentFormat()` first, then applies woco patches (body.start, body.end, description.end, portless, TDD blocks, placeholders)\n   - `renderAgentTemplate()` supports custom agent names\n   - `ensureAgentDefinition()` checks for agent files\n\n4. **`src/config.ts`** — Already has `AgentRegistryConfig` type and defaults:\n   - `mode: \"auto\"`, `source: \"msitarzewski/agency-agents\"`, `cacheDir: \"agents-cache\"`, `cacheTTL: 24h`\n\n5. **`src/lib/tasks.ts`** — Task type already has `agent_type?: string` and `agent?: string` fields\n\n6. **`src/lib/state.ts`** — AgentState already has `agent_name: string | null` and `agent_type: string | null`\n\n7. **`src/commands/launch.ts`** (1698 lines) — Already fully integrated:\n   - Resolves specialized agents via `prepareAgentDefinitions()` before launch\n   - Passes `agentResolutions` through to `launchSingleHeadless()` and `launchWaveInteractive()`\n   - `launchSingleHeadless()` writes patched agent to worktree via `writeAgentToWorktree()`\n   - Agent name override flows: CLI `--agent` > task `agent` field > registry `agent_type`\n   - Preflight confirmation UI for agent resolutions\n\n8. **`src/index.ts`** — CLI already supports `--agent` flag, parsed and passed to `cmdLaunch()`\n\n9. **`src/lib/launcher.ts`** — `launchHeadless()` already accepts `agentName` option and passes it via `--agent` flag\n\n10. **`src/lib/preflight.ts`** — Already has `tuiPreflightConfirm()` and `consolePreflightConfirm()` for agent review\n\n**The agency-agents repo structure** has categories as top-level dirs (engineering/, design/, marketing/, testing/, etc.) with markdown files like `engineering-frontend-developer.md`. Each file has YAML frontmatter with `name`, `description`, `color`, `emoji`, `vibe` fields.\n\n## Accomplished\n\n**The entire feature appears to be already implemented.** All the pieces are in place:\n- ✅ Dynamic pulling from agency-agents GitHub repo\n- ✅ Format conversion (agency-agents → woco)\n- ✅ Local caching with TTL in `.wombo-combo/agents-cache/`\n- ✅ Per-task agent type selection via `agent_type` YAML field\n- ✅ Per-task local agent via `agent` YAML field\n- ✅ CLI `--agent` flag override\n- ✅ Offline mode with stale cache fallback\n- ✅ Fallback to generalist when agent not found\n- ✅ Config for registry mode, source, cache dir, TTL\n- ✅ Integration into launch flow (both headless and interactive)\n- ✅ Preflight confirmation UI\n\n**What still needs to be done:**\n1. **Verify the build passes**: Run `bun run build` to confirm everything compiles\n2. **Check if there are any missing pieces or bugs** — look for TODO comments, incomplete implementations\n3. **Ensure tests exist** if applicable\n4. **Make any necessary commits** if changes are needed\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n### Core implementation files (all read, all appear complete):\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/agent-registry.ts` — Registry fetch, cache, resolve\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/format-converter.ts` — Agency-agents → woco format conversion\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/templates.ts` — Agent template rendering and patching\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/config.ts` — Config types including AgentRegistryConfig\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/tasks.ts` — Task type with agent_type/agent fields\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/state.ts` — AgentState with agent_name/agent_type fields\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/commands/launch.ts` — Launch command with full registry integration\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/launcher.ts` — Process spawning with agentName support\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/index.ts` — CLI entry point with --agent flag\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/preflight.ts` — Preflight confirmation (referenced but not read)\n\n### Template files:\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/templates/` — Directory with generalist-agent.md, patch files\n\n### Project config:\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/package.json`\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/AGENTS.md`\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/tsconfig.json` (not read yet)\n\n### Tests:\n- `/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/tests/` — Directory exists (not read yet)","time":{"start":1773439991696,"end":1773439991696}}}
