n task-level `agent` field |\n| AgentState persistence | `src/lib/state.ts` lines 59-64: `agent_name` and `agent_type` fields |\n| Launcher passes to opencode | `src/lib/launcher.ts` line 51: `agentName?: string` in `LaunchOptions`; line 117: passes `--agent` flag |\n| Task normalization | `src/lib/task-store.ts` lines 226-231: cleans null/empty agent fields |\n| Schema validation | `src/lib/task-schema.ts` lines 187-192: validates `agent` field |\n\n---\n\n## Requirement 5: Offline mode with cached agents and fallback behavior\n\n**Status: FULLY IMPLEMENTED**\n\n| What | Where |\n|---|---|\n| Resolution flow (cache-first) | `src/lib/agent-registry.ts` lines 424-493: `resolveAgentForTask()` — checks cache with TTL, fetches if stale/missing |\n| Stale cache fallback on fetch failure | `src/lib/agent-registry.ts` lines 473-488: uses stale cache + emits warning |\n| Warning on stale cache usage | `src/lib/agent-registry.ts` lines 475-479 |\n| Generalist fallback on total failure | `src/lib/agent-registry.ts` lines 526-537: in `prepareAgentDefinitions()`, catches individual failures, falls back to generalist with warning |\n| Registry-disabled mode | `src/lib/agent-registry.ts` line 430: returns generalist immediately when registry is disabled |\n\n---\n\n## Preflight Confirmation UI\n\n**Status: FULLY IMPLEMENTED**\n\n| What | Where |\n|---|---|\n| Console mode (non-TTY) | `src/lib/preflight.ts` lines 59-105: `consolePreflightConfirm()` — plain text task-to-agent mapping with y/n prompt |\n| TUI mode (TTY) | `src/lib/preflight.ts` lines 130-298: `tuiPreflightConfirm()` — blessed TUI with navigation, mode cycling (Tab), agent rejection (x key) |\n| Integration in launch pipeline | `src/commands/launch.ts` lines 1591-1604: shown when agentResolutions exist; uses TUI if TTY + not `--no-tui`, else console |\n\n---\n\n## Agent Template Patching\n\n**Status: FULLY IMPLEMENTED**\n\n| What | Where |\n|---|---|\n| Patch: description suffix | `src/templates/wc-patch.description.