{"type":"text","timestamp":1773440472297,"sessionID":"ses_316bba7bfffeeA1IqckNkl9JmJ","part":{"id":"prt_ce949f469001ZAh1iUeHhDoSQG","sessionID":"ses_316bba7bfffeeA1IqckNkl9JmJ","messageID":"msg_ce949edd0001Ecjw8geNToqFGQ","type":"text","text":"I found two concrete gaps that should be fixed:\n\n### Gap 1: `launchInteractive` doesn't pass `--agent` flag\nIn `launchInteractive()` (launcher.ts line 253-260), the `agentName` option is accepted but never used. The headless version uses it at line 117, but interactive doesn't.\n\n### Gap 2: `resume.ts` doesn't re-resolve agents from registry for relaunched agents\nWhen agents with `agent_type` are relaunched during resume, their specialized agent definitions aren't re-resolved or re-written to the worktree. For headless, `launchSingleHeadless` will use `agent.agent_name` for the CLI flag but won't write the agent markdown file. For interactive, neither the CLI flag nor the agent file is used.\n\nLet me fix both:","time":{"start":1773440472297,"end":1773440472297}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773440472843,"sessionID":"ses_316bba7bfffeeA1IqckNkl9JmJ","part":{"id":"prt_ce94a08e2001k5SD76ee3Rpd4v","sessionID":"ses_316bba7bfffeeA1IqckNkl9JmJ","messageID":"msg_ce949edd0001Ecjw8geNToqFGQ","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01Gosj474eKur5LSmHbppE8i","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/lib/launcher.ts","oldString":"  const ocArgs = [\n    agentBin,\n    \"--dir\", JSON.stringify(opts.worktreePath),\n  ];\n\n  if (opts.model) {\n    ocArgs.push(\"--model\", JSON.stringify(opts.model));\n  }\n\n  const muxCmd = envPrefix ? `${envPrefix} ${ocArgs.join(\" \")}` : ocArgs.join(\" \");\n","newString":"  const ocArgs = [\n    agentBin,\n    \"--dir\", JSON.stringify(opts.worktreePath),\n  ];\n\n  // Pass agent name if specified (specialized agent from registry or per-task override)\n  if (opts.agentName) {\n    ocArgs.push(\"--agent\", JSON.stringify(opts.agentName));\n  }\n\n  if (opts.model) {\n    ocArgs.push(\"--model\", JSON.stringify(opts.model));\n  }\n\n  const muxCmd = envPrefix ? `${envPrefix} ${ocArgs.join(\" \")}` : ocArgs.join(\" \");\n"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"src/lib/launcher.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/dynamic-agent-types/src/commands/launch.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":32,"character":2},"end":{"line":32,"character":19}},"message":"'areAgentDepsReady' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":37,"character":7},"end":{"line":37,"character":29}},"message":"'SerializedSchedulePlan' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":55,"character":2},"end":{"line":55,"character":18}},"message":"'retryInteractive' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"star